  # Error Cases Testing
  
  This file tests various error scenarios for Eve API endpoints.
  
  ## Test Cases Covered:
  1. Unauthorized access (no auth token)
  2. Invalid journal ID
  3. Invalid session ID
  4. Non-existent resources
  
  ## Note
  This is the first test case (unauthorized access).
  Additional error tests would be added as separate requests
  to cover different error scenarios.
  
  ## Expected Behaviors:
  - 401 for unauthorized requests
  - 404 for non-existent resources
  - 400 for malformed requests
  - 422 for validation errors
}
